name: Cão da Meia Noite
description: Midnight Dog is a huge dog with black fur. It is common to see this creature in cemeteries, it is said that he always appears to console people who go at night. His most common appearance is similar to wolves, it is said that his appearance can often be quite frightening, but generally he doesn't attack people if they don't come his way.<Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
